sequenceDiagram
    actor Tick as Sync Interval
    participant Node as NodeA
    participant Peer as NodeB

    Tick->>Node: sync tick

    Note over Node,Peer: Step 1 — fetch peer IBLT
    Node->>Peer: GetIBLT
    Peer-->>Node: encoded IBLT

    Note over Node: Step 2 — subtract IBLTs and decode<br/>

    alt diff decodes
        Note over Node,Peer: Step 3 — push and pull concurrently
        Node->>Peer: PushEntries (onlyLocal)
        Peer->>Peer: ApplyDelta per entry
        Peer-->>Node: PushAck
        Node->>Peer: PullEntries (onlyRemote)
        Peer-->>Node: stream entries
        Node->>Node: ApplyDelta per entry
    else fallback
        Note over Node,Peer: Full-state fallback
        Node->>Peer: PushEntries (entire local store)
        Peer->>Peer: ApplyDelta per entry
        Node->>Peer: PullEntries (entire peer store)
        Peer-->>Node: stream entries
        Node->>Node: ApplyDelta per entry
    end
